org.societies.android.api.cis
Class SocialContract.PeopleActivity

java.lang.Object
  org.societies.android.api.cis.SocialContract.PeopleActivity
Enclosing class:
SocialContract
public static final class SocialContract.PeopleActivity
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a table containing all the activities that are added to the activity feeds for people. You can search the table using a specific user's global ID as feed owner ID.

Author:
Babak dot Farshchian at sintef dot no

public static final java.lang.String _ID
